# Media binaries are kept on disk (so injection works locally) but NOT committed.
# They are large and heavily duplicated (~22 MB, dominated by full-bleed photos on
# a couple of collage slides), and most media-bearing slides are curation-delete
# candidates rather than reusable logic diagrams. The shapes.xml.gz vectors ARE
# committed — 204 of 223 diagrams are pure-vector and fully self-contained.
#
# After curating, force-add the media for any media-bearing diagram you keep:
#     git add -f <key>/media/
*/media/

# The repo root .gitignore excludes *.gz (build artifacts). Our shapes.xml.gz is
# intentional diagram content, so re-include it explicitly.
!*/shapes.xml.gz

